{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 7 summarizes these challenges and points the way for future research.",
    "Challenges in knowledge graph construction 1.",
    "Difficulty in information fusion: LLM-KG fusion encounters fundamental representational conflicts between the implicit statistical patterns of LLMs and the explicit symbolic structures of KGs.",
    "This mismatch systematically disrupts entity linking consistency.",
    "Current hybrid approaches suffer three core limitations: introduce semantic noise during context augmentation (Ayoola et al., 2022; Xin et al., 2024), remain constrained by LLM training biases in candidate generation (Ding Y. et al., 2024), and create new modality-specific dependencies in multimodal fusion (Liu Q. et al., 2024)."
  ]
}